Introduction

Choi Jungeun is a South Korean singer and dancer under WAKEONE.

In 2020, she participated in the Mnet' survival show "CAP-TEEN", but was sadly unable to win.

In 2024, she was a contestant on Mnet' survival show I-LAND2: N/a, where she ended up ranking 1st place in the final with 823,393 votes, thus securing her spot as a member of the final group, izna.

Choi Jungeun made her debut with the group on November 25, 2024, with the release of their first mini album titled "N/a".
